什么决定了Formula 1的速度？¶

14307130391

2015-2017Formula 1F1

AbstractThis report is based on a csv file which includes the data from 2015 to the 2017 season, and consists of tables describing constructors, race drivers, lap times, pit stops and more. The main tasks are to visualize the data, and then hunt for the changing trend of race speed, and explore the relations between race drivers. constructors, the accumulated points of both and race speed.

: Formular 1
